# ============================================================
# Oath Purification Journey - GitIgnore
# 策略: 黑名单 + 白名单，仅保留 Scripts 代码及必要配置
# ============================================================

# --- 1. 忽略所有内容 ---
*

# --- 2. 白名单：Git 管理文件自身 ---
!.gitignore

# --- 3. 白名单：项目文档 ---
!project-overview.md

# --- 4. 白名单：Unity 包依赖清单（没有它代码无法定位 API） ---
!Packages/
!Packages/manifest.json
!Packages/packages-lock.json

# --- 5. 白名单：项目版本信息 ---
!ProjectSettings/
!ProjectSettings/ProjectVersion.txt

# --- 6. 白名单：源代码 ---
!Assets/
!Assets/Scripts/
!Assets/Scripts/**
